issues.description: The addGuestStudents method in the solution only accepts a single int parameter, but the problem statement and UML diagram require two parameters (an int and a String reason). This parameter mismatch will cause student tests expecting the String argument to fail.
issues.suggested_fix: Change the signature of addGuestStudents in Lecture.java to include both parameters, e.g., public void addGuestStudents(int numberOfNewGuestStudents, String reason), so it matches the UML and task description, and then handle the reason appropriately.
